{"tid":2050130,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國教授：一人一短片 同美國國務院一齊悼念天安門","createTime":"2020-06-04T02:40:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-04T06:53:21.000Z","uid":35776,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9137165c7e97f58da2db1c52c4e65f078cf671e8","tid":2050130,"uid":35776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T02:40:01.000Z","msg":"美國教授：悼念天安門<br />\n今年六四是30周年，亦是美國國務院首次為六四舉行網上追悼會。就讓我們一起向美國國務院表示心意。<br />\n方法如下:<br />\n國務院請參與者錄製15到30秒的視頻，拍攝自己拿著蠟燭的畫面(繪圖也可以)，簡述如何受到天安門示威者的鼓舞，或者每天為爭取什麼自由而奮鬥；並以#TiananmenVigil為標籤，將內容上載到個人社交媒體，可轉推國務院@StateDept和@StateDRL視頻。 <br />\n販民係無用暗共，不要再跟著販民走。歐洲和日本只是對香港國安法閒話幾句，沒有行動。現在只有美國能夠讓我們成功。<br />\n為了死傷及被虐打被強姦的義士，我們一定要去馬。這是去馬機會，今日就一齊動手，讓全世界看看香港人的堅持和決心。<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/QsTJQ9Y\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FQsTJQ9Y&h=68197b5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"527b51a641f0188371e79495a7b9b9abfac1e31a","tid":2050130,"uid":35776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T02:41:38.000Z","msg":"補圖<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cPcRzgN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcPcRzgN.png&h=4b75d2bb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"77c63f8273ad0eefd076d9da982c1c15b3dbcfd1","tid":2050130,"uid":60539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"527b51a641f0188371e79495a7b9b9abfac1e31a","tid":2050130,"uid":35776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T02:41:38.000Z","msg":"補圖<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cPcRzgN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcPcRzgN.png&h=4b75d2bb&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T02:44:13.000Z","msg":"美國教授做咩唔出得樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27874458472f9c43710991ac9778f3787f5e4ca2","tid":2050130,"uid":35776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77c63f8273ad0eefd076d9da982c1c15b3dbcfd1","tid":2050130,"uid":60539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quo